item.title: How to change my home?
item.dc:creator: @KillinXxSMile KillinXxSMile
item.description:
@KillinXxSMile wrote:

I’m gonna go off and guess that your running a 317 since you sound knew to java

to change your home just change the coords of your home command.
but if you meant you want to change where you spawn when you first log on
go to your player class
and search for where you spawn on log in now
you should see something like
teleportToX = ####;
teleportToY = ####;
all you have to do is change the
teleportToX = ####;
with the x coordinate of where you want to start off
and
teleportToY = ####;
with the y coordinate of where you want to start off
